[INT-009] KNOWLEDGE FILES — DAEMON-GENERATED CONTENT TRACKED
  Path: agentin/knowledge/
  Tracked files:
    llm_rankings_2026.md                         ← daemon-generated
    multiagent/foundation_architecture.md        ← daemon-generated
    multiagent/foundation_tools_inventory.md     ← daemon-generated
    multiagent/skill_monitoring_debugging.md     ← daemon-generated
    multiagent/skill_permission_contracts.md     ← daemon-generated
  The knowledge/library/ and knowledge/staging/ have .gitignore but the root
